Facebook Notifier version 0.1

Currently only checks for new messages/friend requests

This is my first attempt at a Cocoa OS X app. Please let me know if you have any comments or suggestions!

Based on example code from:
http://files.semaja2.net/NSStatusItem%20-%20ObjC.html#TOC6944 

Facebook functionality requires the use of MKAbeFook:
See http://pointlesscrap.net/mkabefook/

Make sure to add the MKAbeFook framework
